{
  "stem": "20848.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were ready to put-- to blow it up when the-- when the whats-the-name came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the liberation came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we thought they're going to do the same in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they never managed to do-- to do anything because they were wearing white bands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day they all vanished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just-- just went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we found ourselves without SS, and all the [GERMAN] went with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I said [GERMAN], the kapos, the Lageraltestes, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people who had big jobs there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they probably would-- were scared that they would be, you know, punished from the prisoners later on-- What about Schmidt?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's why I'm bringing it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she has never done anybody any harm, but she went too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was searching for her, looking for her, because I really wanted to help her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to save her life now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I couldn't find her anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I never, ever heard of her again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one day--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
